These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, time-travel, western, fantasy
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, roller, train, jet-ski
4 different games are played: go, billiard, mah-jongg, scrabble
City: colone, berlin, hamburg, liverpool
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person playing go##1
 3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person driving the train is between the person traveling to colone and the person playing scrabble##2
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 9. the person playing go is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
10. the person traveling to colone is between the person driving the train and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing billiard and the person watching western movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | coffee       | lemonade  | almond-milk |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| Movie-Genre         | time-travel  | disaster      | western   | fantasy     |
| Transport           | roller | trike | train   | jet-ski     |
| Game   | billiard    | mah-jongg         | go | scrabble         |
| City         | liverpool     | colone     | berlin  | hamburg       |

