.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, watermelon, garlic, strawberry
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, goldfish, fish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk, gospel
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, backgammon, bridge
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, journalist, coach, firefighter
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person eating garlic and the police-officer##2
 2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 3. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person drinking almond-milk and the coach##2
 5. the fan of disco is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the coach is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person eating strawberry##2
 9. the owner of the frog is the person eating strawberry##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
11. the fan of disco is the owner of the goldfish##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
13. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the journalist##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | fanta       | soy-milk   | almond-milk |
| Food         | pumpkin     | garlic   | strawberry    | watermelon  |
| Pet   | chinchilla    | goldfish | frog   | fish     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       | electronic | folk        |
| Game   | bridge | backgammon   | mah-jongg     | snooker    |
| Job     | journalist       | coach        | firefighter      | police-officer        |

